951
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:11,830
Bakit wala kang sinasabi?

952
00:40:13,740 --> 00:40:15,870
Hindi mo rin isinara ang bintanang iyon.

953
00:40:16,230 --> 00:40:17,000
Sobrang basa sa loob.

954
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:19,260
Bakit hindi mo binuksan ang dehumidifier?

955
00:40:32,890 --> 00:40:34,360
Ano bang problema ko
bumili ng isang pares ng bota?

956
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:36,070
kailangan ko
magdala ng ganoon kalaking tiyan araw-araw,

957
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,230
at napakabigat nito.

958
00:40:39,880 --> 00:40:41,080
Sinabi sa akin ng doktor...

959
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:44,370
para pumunta sa ospital bukas

960
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:48,290
para sa pinahusay na CT scan ng tiyan.

961
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:52,320
Pwede mo ba akong samahan?

962
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:01,510
anong mali?

